               <p>Before Mr. Justice Best.</p>
               <p>1030. 
               
                  <persName id="t18230910-39-defend462" type="defendantName">
                     SAMUEL 
                     HADDEN
                  <interp inst="t18230910-39-defend462" type="surname" value="HADDEN"></interp>
