             was indicted for <rs id="t18230910-39-off216" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230910-39-off216" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-39-off216" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230910-39-cd217" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-39-off216 t18230910-39-cd217"></join>, at St. Pancras, one coat, value 3 l. 10 s., one handkerchief, value 1 s., and two pair of gloves, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230910-39-victim464" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Ashdown
                        <interp inst="t18230910-39-victim464" type="surname" value="Ashdown"></interp>
